```{r bileducts 32989224, include=FALSE}

PMID_32989224 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32989224', database = 'PubMed')

PubMed_32989224 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32989224$eprint)

doi_32989224 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32989224$doi)
```
